history.provenance:
‘Summa totalis libri’ (fol. iiiv, s. xv;
                     some further s. xv pen-trials appear on fol.
                        iv).

supportDesc.collation:
12–1412 1514.
                                 Boxed catchwords at the gutter;
                              no signatures.

decoDesc.decoNote:
At the head, an unflourished 4-line red lombard;
                           the text divided by red paraphs and red-slashed capitals; index entries
                           introduced by alternate 1-line red and blue lombards.
